template: SELECT MIN(keyword.id) AS keyword_id FROM aka_title, cast_info, movie_keyword, movie_companies, person_info, movie_info_idx, char_name, info_type, name, movie_info, aka_name, title, keyword WHERE aka_name.person_id = name.id AND aka_title.movie_id = title.id AND cast_info.person_id = name.id AND cast_info.movie_id = title.id AND cast_info.person_role_id = char_name.id AND info_type.id = movie_info.info_type_id AND info_type.id = movie_info_idx.info_type_id AND info_type.id = person_info.info_type_id AND keyword.id = movie_keyword.keyword_id AND movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info_idx.movie_id = title.id AND movie_keyword.movie_id = title.id AND person_info.person_id = name.id AND title.production_year > %s AND movie_companies.note LIKE %s AND title.production_year < %s AND person_info.note = %s AND movie_info_idx.info < %s AND info_type.info = %s;
